      "content": {
        "text": "KITCHEN - CONTINUOUS\n\n[Approx. Timestamp: 00:01:30]\nEmma pours water. The whisper again\u2014closer, like breath on her neck.\n\nWHISPER (O.S.)...stay...\n\nEmma spins. Nothing. She laughs nervously.\n\nEMMA\nOld house. Just the wind.\n\nShe heads upstairs.",
