        "duration": 26
      },
      "content": {
        "text": "LIVING ROOM - NIGHT\n\n[Approx. Timestamp: 00:05:00]\nEmma searches frantically. Calls out.\n\nEMMA\nLily! This isn't funny!\n\nThe whispers grow\u2014multiple voices now, overlapping, childlike but wrong.\n\nWHISPERS (O.S.)...she's ours now... she likes it here...\n\nEmma grabs her phone\u2014 no signal. She runs to the front door. Locked. She twists the knob violently.\n\nEMMA\nOpen! Come on!\n\nThe lights flicker. Shadows stretch unnaturally long across the walls.",
