      "content": {
        "text": "BASEMENT STAIRS - NIGHT\n\n[Approx. Timestamp: 00:07:30]\nEmma, flashlight in hand, descends slowly. The whispers lead her down.\n\nWHISPERS...down here... she's waiting...\n\nAt the bottom: the basement is empty except for an old mirror covered in dust. Emma approaches.\n\nShe wipes the glass. Her reflection stares back\u2014but it's not moving with her. The reflection smiles.\n\nREFLECTION EMMA\n(soft, eerie)\nYou've been gone so long, Emma. We missed you.\n\nEmma backs away. The mirror cracks\u2014slow spiderweb fr",
