      "content": {
        "text": "ures.\n\nSuddenly, LILY'S VOICE from behind the mirror.\n\nLILY (O.S.)\nMommy... help...\n\nEmma smashes the mirror with her elbow. Glass shatters. Darkness swallows the room.\n\nThe whispers become screams\u2014inhuman.\n\nEMMA\n(screaming)\nGive her back!\n\nBlackout. Only the sound of rain... and one last whisper.\n\nWHISPER (O.S.)...she's home now...",
